          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Mortgage Forgiveness Tax Relief Act </b><b>of 2019</b></p> <p> This bill modifies the requirements for calculating taxable income to extend through 2019 the exclusion from gross income of income attributable to the discharge of indebtedness on a principal residence.</p>]]></text>
